```

### 4. Grant Acceso Empresa-Cliente

```bash
curl -X POST https://auth.test.acceleralia.com/admin/access/company-client \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "Cookie: admin_session=YOUR_SESSION_TOKEN" \
  -d '{
    "company_id": "2",
    "client_id": "crm-system"
  }'
```

### 5. Información para Guardar

```json
{
  "client_id": "crm-system",
  "client_secret": "CRM_Secret_2024!",
  "redirect_uri": "https://crm.test.acceleralia.com/api/auth/callback",
  "post_logout_redirect_uri": "https://crm.test.acceleralia.com",
  "issuer_url": "https://auth.test.acceleralia.com",
